(77752, 141441, 0, 1, 'Chocolate Tears', '就在白色走廊的盡頭 各種瓶子接著籠頭\n有些勁辣有些苦澀 這瓶巧克力在 流\n就在白色行李箱裡頭 不同名字不同顏色\n有些滾燙有些冰冷 這瓶巧克力在 流\n\n巧克力眼淚 我為我調配 一人獨享 午夜的甜點\n巧克力眼淚 甜蜜在溶解 說你不配 抹去我的淚\n巧克力眼淚 不想被瞭解 說話好累 它 好累  情緒代謝 不需要理會\n\n不容你吞食 甜蜜的傷口 請慢慢 - 舔食 它\n承受你的罪 稀釋你的痛 巧克力 - - 眼淚\n', '2014-08-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 7, '', '', 223, '', 'Leslie', 'Leslie', 'Peggy Hsu 許郁翎', 'Leslie', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-31 11:49:44', '2015-03-12 14:08:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77753, 141441, 0, 1, 'Sing a Song for Me Tonight', '', '2014-08-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 7, '車燈像流星劃過指尖 合起手掌看見你的側臉\n分手到第幾天 才能夠體會 擦肩而過的不是遺憾\n寧願和天花板聊個天 也不想上網或和誰見面\n還不想要聽見 不想有關連 不想捨棄剩餘的尊嚴\n\nSing a song for me, tonight. 說我還值得愛\nSing a song for me, tonight. 讓我不再不安\n\n曾經我多麼依賴 捨不得說晚安 （say goodbye)\n黑夜裡我唱起歌 月光  透了進來\n捷運錯過兩站才發現 情緒超載我都覺得討厭\n好想離開這邊 穿越那時間 只留下快樂的感覺\n', '', 206, '', 'Leslie', 'Leslie', 'Peggy Hsu 許郁翎', 'Leslie', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-31 11:51:06', '2015-03-12 14:08:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77754, 141441, 0, 1, 'She Has a Face Like Him', '', '2014-08-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 7, 'the chipping door opened. In pigtail she appeared. \nThe dying light flickered. She has a face like him. \nCome pledge with both eyes closed. In blood and gull she writes. \nNo more shall you suffer. She has a face like him.\nThe smooth earlobe spoke. How accessories curse.\nLike a silent tear drop. Keep her dry and cracking.\nThe smooth earlobe spoke. What it takes to believe.\nLike a secret tear drop. Bend her knee and her back. \n\nChorus:\nTake out the rusty metal. Let it bleed till it won’t heal.\nThis is not a punishment. Piercing make you girl next life. (x2)\n\nShe has a face like him (x8) \n', '', 208, '', 'Leslie', 'Leslie', 'Peggy Hsu 許郁翎', 'Leslie', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-31 11:53:29', '2015-03-12 14:08:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77755, 141441, 0, 1, 'Tree', '', '2014-08-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 7, '從前有棵樹默默的守護小男孩的路途\n男孩迷了路 感覺好無助脫了鞋爬上了樹\n他閉着眼哭訴 不為人知的感觸\n\nCome on boy. 為什麼迷惘  靠近我 不要再回頭\n然後你會很快樂 你會真的很快樂\nCome on boy. 為什麼流浪  靠近我  設王位在這\n然後我會很快樂 我是真的快樂\n\n男孩離開後 越走越孤獨想不起那棵樹\n停不下腳步 任絕望擺佈  樹遠遠不停地哭 \n\nCome on boy. 砍下我的手讓我承擔你的難過\n然後你會很快樂　你會非常的快樂\nCome on boy. 砍下我的手 不再擁抱你的傷痕\n痛楚也能很快樂我是真的快樂\n\n男人砍下樹 造艘小船尋找張陌生 溫柔的臉\n最後將我全 部都點燃只要你看見最後的溫暖\n', '', 191, '', 'Leslie', 'Leslie', 'Peggy Hsu 許郁翎', 'Leslie', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-31 11:54:56', '2015-03-12 14:08:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77756, 141441, 0, 1, 'Stupid Girl', '', '2014-08-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 3, 'Stupid. Stupid. Stupid. Stupid. Stupid girl.\nStupid. Stupid. Stupid. Stupid. Stupid girl.\n(You say) Uh, oh. Uh, oh. Who’s that girl?\nOh, both you and I, we know that girl.\n(You don’t have to ask. Oh, you’re that girl.)\nSold your soul with a nod,\nand betrayed your heart for those you love.\nBut little did you know\nThat the reason they like you\nWas because the stupid, stupid girl you are.\nHurt yourself without cause.\nTook a blow to protect those you love.\nBut little did you know\nThat the people you adore\nWas using the stupid, stupid girl you are.\nI don’t want to know the reason why you\nWant to fall in love with people who put\nPrice tag on your soul?\nWhat the matter?\nIf you wanna cry just go back home.\n', '', 217, '', 'Leslie', 'Leslie', 'Peggy Hsu 許郁翎', 'Leslie', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-31 11:56:21', '2015-03-12 14:08:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
